(1) Ocean View Cemetery (Staten Island): A view of the clock-tower building near the entrance on the north side of Amboy Road, at Hopkins Avenue.

About 1905.

By Mulford Simonson.
From Staten Island Museum Collection through P. L. Sperr.

(2) Another view at a later date.

1924.

P. L. Sperr.
